---
/**
 * categories/[category].astro — Enhanced PupWiki category hub page
 *
 * Goals:
 * - No Amazon/ProductGrid/products.json dependency.
 * - AWIN-first monetization pipeline.
 * - Strong internal linking to breed-specific guides, tools and related categories.
 * - Mobile-first layout using PupWiki global design tokens.
 * - Safer wording: no unsupported “expert verified” claims.
 */

